the new @glowrecipe glass balms are here!! 💖

baby, when they say glass, they mean it!! the shine on these is absolutely insane like wowza. they smell so yummy too!! with all the lippies on the market, i wouldn’t say these are a “need” or anything revolutionary but if you love a high shine balm that smells yummy and feels hydrating, these will fit the bill for sure 👏🏻 so happy to see the brand venturing into more color cosmetics overall 👀 

are you eyeing this new launch? 

*press samples—brand ambassador 
…..

#glowrecipe #glowrecipeglassbalm #newatsephora #lipbalm #lippies #koreanskincare #officialglowgangambassador

what’s life without a little mystery…🖤

the newest scent from @bonparfumeur is for those who love to smell a little dark, mysterious, and alluring 🐈‍⬛ this is described as blending the warmth of amber and vanilla with aromatic cypress and tumult pepper and bitter orange and zesty grapefruit. 

while my hopes were high for this one, i sadly only got a black licorice and basil note to my nose with a powdery finish that just didn’t sit quite right on my skin. i think this would smell amazing on someone else, but for me, it just didn’t pan out. it’s perfectly unisex and i could see this being amazing in the cooler months or on date night!! 

you can shop this exclusively at @luckyscent ◡̈ 

if you’ve tried this one, i’d love to know your thoughts!! 💭
